## 🏗️ ARCHITECTURE COMPLIANCE

### Tech Stack Requirements
- **Mobile**: Android Jetpack Compose, Hilt (DI), Coroutines, Ktor/Retrofit
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Storage, Edge Functions, Realtime)
- **Design**: Bento UI, Glassmorphism, Material 3
- **Security**: Row Level Security (RLS), Role-Based Access Control

### Clean Architecture Principles
- Repository pattern untuk data access
- ViewModels untuk state management
- Dependency Injection dengan Hilt
- Single Responsibility Principle
- Separation of concerns

## 💰 FINANCIAL DATA REQUIREMENTS

- **Mandatory**: Gunakan BigDecimal/Decimal untuk semua nilai finansial
- Property prices, KPR amounts, Down payments
- Transaction amounts, Commission calculations
- Tidak menggunakan Float/Double untuk financial values

## 📱 PHASE EXECUTION RULES

### Sequential Development
- Phase 1: Foundation & DI ✅
- Phase 2: Database Schema & RBAC ✅  
- Phase 3: Core Repositories ✅
- Phase 4: Role-Based Navigation ✅
- Phase 5: Base UI Dashboards 🔄
- Phase 6-25: Sesuai protocol

### Completion Criteria
- Setiap phase harus dikonfirmasi dengan "PHASE [X] COMPLETE"
- User approval sebelum melanjutkan ke phase berikutnya
- Testing dan validation untuk setiap implementasi

## 🔐 SECURITY REQUIREMENTS

### Row Level Security (RLS)
- Customer: Access own data only
- Marketing: View customers, manage units & dossiers
- Legal: View all documents, verify compliance
- Finance: Manage transactions, approve payments
- BOD: Full system access

### Data Protection
- UUID-based primary keys
- JWT-based authentication
- Role-based API endpoints
- Encrypted storage untuk sensitive documents

